snippet.title: Chandrayaan 3 ने भेजा संदेश, हर हिंदुस्तानी को सुनना चाहिए | ISRO | Chandrayaan 3 updates
snippet.description:
Chandrayaan 3 ने भेजा संदेश, हर हिंदुस्तानी को सुनना चाहिए | ISRO | Chandrayaan-3 updates | Chandrayaan 3 live | Chandrayaan 3 Update
----

#chandryaan3 #isro #chandryan 

Chandrayaan 3 ने भेजा संदेश, हर हिंदुस्तानी को सुनना चाहिए | ISRO | Chandrayaan-3 updates | Chandrayaan 3 live | Chandrayaan 3 Update

चंद्रयान 3 (Chandrayaan 3) ने कमाल कर दिया है...इसरो (ISRO) के साथ पूरी दुनिया को जिस पल का इंतजार था...वो पल अब आ गया है... Chandrayaan-3 ने अग्निपरिक्षा को पास कर लिया है...भारत के लिए ये किसी बड़ी जीत से कम नहीं है...भारत की अंतरिक्ष में बढ़ती धमक की सबसे बड़ी खबर चंद्रमा के ऑर्बिट से आई है.... 5 जुलाई को Chandrayaan 3 ने जैसे ही चांद की कक्षा में कदम रखा, उसने धरती पर इसरो सेंटर को सबसे पहले जो संदेश भेजा उसे हर भारतीय को जरूर सुनना चाहिए

snippet.title: OMG2 - Official Trailer | Akshay Kumar, Pankaj Tripathi, Yami Gautam | Amit Rai | In Theatres Aug 11
snippet.description:
११ अगस्त का बुलावा है
आ रहे हैं हम 🙏

A sequel to the much-celebrated OMG-Oh My God, OMG2 is a social comedy/drama starring Akshay Kumar, Pankaj Tripathi and Yami Gautam in lead roles. 

The film will release in theatres on August 11, 2023. 

Book your tickets on: 
BookMyShow: https://bookmy.show/OMG-2
Paytm: https://m.paytm.me/m_omg2

Synopsis: 
Life is bliss until one day Kanti Sharan Mudgal’s son Vivek is blamed for immoral conduct and expelled from school. Overwhelmed, Kanti plans to leave town until a divine intervention leads him to seek justice by taking those responsible to court.

Viacom18 Studio presents ​in association with Cape Of Good Films ​& Wakaoo Films 
A Cape Of Good Films and Wakaoo Films production ​
“OMG 2” 
Written & Directed by Amit Rai 
Produced by ​Aruna Bhatia, Cape Of Good Films 
Produced by ​Viacom18 Studios, Jyoti Deshpande, Ajit Andhare 
Produced by ​Swaroop Paresh Rawal, Hemal A. Thakkar​
Produced by ​Vipul D. Shah, Ashwin Varde, Rajesh Bahl
Creative Producer: Dr Chandraprakash Dwivedi 
Co-Producer: Vedant Baali   
Story, Screenplay & Dialogues: Amit Rai

Music by Vikram Montrose, Hansraj Raghuwanshi, Djstrings, Pranaay, Sandesh Shandilya 
Lyrics by Shekhar Astitwa, Hansraj Raghuwanshi, Djstrings, Kabeer Shukla, Ginny Diwan, Sandesh Shandilya

snippet.title: Marvel Studios’ I Am Groot Season 2 | Official Trailer | Disney+
snippet.description:
You woodn't beleaf what Groot gets up to in Season 🌳🌳!

Marvel Studios’ #IAmGroot Season 2 is streaming September 6 on Disney+. #NationalTreeDay

Five new “I Am Groot” shorts are heading to Disney+ beginning Sept. 6.

The troublemaking twig returns to mischief in the second season of “I Am Groot.” This time, Baby Groot finds himself exploring the universe and beyond aboard the Guardians’ spaceships, coming face-to-face—or nose-to-nose—with new and colorful creatures and environments. Vin Diesel is back as the voice of Groot in five all-new shorts. Kirsten Lepore, writer/director of season one, returns in the same capacity for season two. The supervising producer is Danielle Costa; producers are Craig Rittenbaum and Alex Scharf; executive producers are Brad Winderbaum, Kevin Feige, Louis D’Esposito, Victoria Alonso and Kirsten Lepore. Dana Vasquez-Eberhardt is co-executive producer.

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Ep 3843 | 7 Aug 2023 | Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3843: Tamatar Ki Chori
--------------------------------------------------------
At the Gokuldham Society, the tomatoes are delivered, and Bhide and Madhvi proceed to inspect them. Madhvi's delivery of the tomatoes to Bhide means that she can now easily fulfill the pickle order, which makes Bhide happy. The hefty tomato basket is too much for Madhvi and Bhide to lift and carry inside. Bhide makes the decision to retire for the night, keeping watch over them until dawn. The newspaper is surprised to see Bhide sleeping on the floor the following morning. Bhide is hesitant to explain why. When Bhide arrives home in the morning, he instructs Madhvi to keep an eye on the tomatoes from the balcony. Later, Madhavi enters the kitchen and engages in conversation with a friend, entirely forgetting about the tomatoes.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3843, 7 Aug 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #15yearsoftmkoc  

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. The hefty tomato basket is too much for Madhvi and Bhide to lift and carry inside. Bhide makes the decision to retire for the night, keeping watch over them until dawn. snippet.title: Onam Shopping with Amma 🌸 | Pothys | Ishaani Krishna.
snippet.description:
#Ad
Hi all 👋🏻 
I thought of categorising each shopping sections by mentioning the time here so that it’s easy for you’ll to focus on the part you want 🤩

1:40 - 3:38 : Ground Floor entrance area. You’ll find laces, brocades, tassels, readymade blouses and linings here.

3:39 - 4:17 : Ground Floor. Cotton Saree Section.

4:20 - 8:48 : 1st Floor. Pure Kanchipuram Saree Section.

8:52 - 12:33 : 1st Floor. Selecting Silk Blouse Peice.

8:53 - 13:35 - 1st Floor. Saw some very beautiful collection of 100% original Balaramapuram Kaithari Sarees

13:38 - 14:37 - 1st Floor. Having a look at some really elegant Banarasi Sarees.

14:39 - 18:01 : 1st Floor. You’d be amazed to see the Bridal wear collection they have🤩 . Not to mention their Bridal gowns as well.

18:08 - 20:17 : 2nd Floor. We first see a few western wear like crop tops, palazzo etc. We then see a lot of branded and non-branded readymade kurtis and salwars. I was also introduced to “Syuta” - an exclusive brand by Pothys.

20:18 - 23:12 : 2nd Floor. Get to see the hugeeee variety of running material collection they have. This is the floor with most crowd. I absolutely loved the materials we saw and purchased.

23:13 - 25:08 : 2nd Floor. Have you heard about their combo offer? They also have a great offer going on for running materials where you’ll get upto 50% off. They also have a special section for Onam trendy collection. Then we also saw a few Ajrakh materials.

25:09 -25:30 : Get a chance to win Hyundai Exter car by purchasing for a minimum of Rs. 3000 🤩

25:41 - 26:09 - They also have a great collection of home appliances 🥰

26:10 - 27:13 - Shop for men’s Ethnic wear, suits and running materials.

27:14 - 28:38 : Men’s dhotis, women’s set mund and set sarees.

28:40 - 30:24 - Electronic Gadgets, phone cases etc.

30:25 - 31:25 : Cosmetics, Womens fancy things, Jewellery, watches, luggage bags etc.

31:26 - 31-35 : Footwear Collections.

31:48 - 32:53 - Billing and going back home 🤗

Hope you enjoyed the video ♥️

snippet.title: Ehraam-e-Junoon Episode 29 Teaser - 7th August 2023 - HAR PAL GEO
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Ehraam-e-Junoon Episode 29 Teaser - 7th August 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

"Ehraam-e-Junoon" follows the story of a young and immensely beautiful girl named Shanzay, who is filled with pride and stubbornness due to her upper-class upbringing. Shanzay believes that money can buy everything, including happiness. 

Despite her high standards, Shanzay is yet to find a man who can impress her until she meets Shayan at an event. Shayan is a handsome young man from a middle-class family, who takes up a job as a pizza delivery boy to make ends meet. Shanzay who is immediately drawn to Shayan wants to provide him with a better lifestyle however, Shayan keeps his distance and refuses to accept any of Shanzay’s advances.

As the story unfolds, Shanzay and Shayan's paths cross again and again, and Shanzay begins to question her beliefs about love and money. Will Shayan be the one to break through Shanzay's walls of pride and stubbornness, or will she continue to chase after superficial things?

The drama serial "Ehraam-e-Junoon" promises to take viewers on a rollercoaster ride of emotions as it explores the themes of love, pride, and class differences.

Writer: Jahanzeb Qamar
Director: Syed Ramish Rizvi
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast :
Imran Abbas as Shani
Neelam Muneer as Shanzay
Nimra Khan as Sajeela
Mahmood Aslam as Kamran
Ismat Zaidi as Kulsoom

Aadi Khan as Jugnu
Birjees Farooqui as Farzana

Mirza Rizwan as Faiq

snippet.description:

1) WWE Summerslam 2023 highlights & full show results in Hindi

— “The American Nightmare” Cody Rhodes def. Brock Lesnar

— Gunther def. Drew McIntyre to retain the WWE Intercontinental Championship
— Seth “Freakin” Rollins def. Finn Bálor to retain the World Heavyweight Championship
— Bianca Belair def. Charlotte Flair and Asuka in a Triple Threat Match to win the WWE Women’s Championship
— IYO SKY def. Bianca Belair to win the WWE Women’s Championship after cashing in her Money in the Bank contract
— Roman Reigns def. Jey Uso in Tribal Combat to retain the Undisputed WWE Universal Championship

snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Ehraam-e-Junoon Episode 28 - [Eng Sub] - Neelam Muneer - Imran Abbas - Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream - 7th August 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Ehraam-e-Junoon Digitally Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream

"Ehraam-e-Junoon" follows the story of a young and immensely beautiful girl named Shanzay, who is filled with pride and stubbornness due to her upper-class upbringing. Shanzay believes that money can buy everything, including happiness. 

Despite her high standards, Shanzay is yet to find a man who can impress her until she meets Shayan at an event. Shayan is a handsome young man from a middle-class family, who takes up a job as a pizza delivery boy to make ends meet. Shanzay who is immediately drawn to Shayan wants to provide him with a better lifestyle however, Shayan keeps his distance and refuses to accept any of Shanzay’s advances.

As the story unfolds, Shanzay and Shayan's paths cross again and again, and Shanzay begins to question her beliefs about love and money. Will Shayan be the one to break through Shanzay's walls of pride and stubbornness, or will she continue to chase after superficial things?

The drama serial "Ehraam-e-Junoon" promises to take viewers on a rollercoaster ride of emotions as it explores the themes of love, pride, and class differences.

Writer: Jahanzeb Qamar
Director: Syed Ramish Rizvi
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

snippet.title: Jethalal और Popatlal में हो गई तकरार! | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Bank Story
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to LIV Comedy: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCBIT1FSJW6yTlzqK-31FDWg?sub_confirmation=1

Bhide calls Madhavi and Sonu for an urgent meeting on their daily expenses. He tells them they are spending too much money. Sonu tells him that she will save money now. Bhide explains to Sonu that he is not telling her to save money but to use it wisely. He tells her that he has kept enough money for her education and marriage. Meanwhile, Tapu comes and tells Sonu not to marry so early. Bhide corrects Tapu and tells him that her parents will take the right decision for her. All men were sitting at Abdul's Soda Shop. Popatlal tells them that Jetha is again late. As soon as Jetha comes Popatlal starts arguing with him. Watch the full episode to know more.

Show Name - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast - Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt
Episode - 2493
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi, Neela Asit Modi

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #livcomedy #tmkoc #comedy2023 #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #comedy #jethalal #taarakmehta 

About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in 'Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

Click here to watch all the fun episodes of TMKOC - Bank Story: 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLSXTaG1fT0cR9p9VQwjI5aMs4C7SD5EYS

Jethalal और Popatlal में हो गई तकरार! | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Bank Story

snippet.title: DREAM GIRL 2 -OFFICIAL TRAILER | Ayushmann K | Ananya P | Ektaa K | Raaj S | In Cinemas 25th August
snippet.description:
Dream Girl ki duniya mein get ready for a rib-tickling kahaani of your sapnon ki rani! 🤩😆

#DreamGirl2Trailer Out Now! 

#25AugustHogaMast
#DreamGirl2 in Cinemas on 25th August.

Tab tak ke liye follow kariyega apni Pooja ko on Instagram and Twitter - 

Instagram - https://instagram.com/pooja___dreamgirl
Twitter - https://twitter.com/Pooja_DreamGirl 

Karam, a small-town boy from Mathura, is struggling every day to pay his father's debt, who has borrowed money from nearly everyone on the planet. On the other hand, he is deeply in love with Pari, whose father has kept the conditions to marry her. To make ends meet, Karam dons as Pooja, which creates wild chaos and a comedy of errors. 

Dream Girl 2 is a rib-tickling and hilariously entertaining story with a compelling ensemble including Annu Kapoor, Paresh Rawal, Vijay Raaz, Rajpal Yadav, Asrani Saab, Manoj Joshi, Abhishek Banerjee, Seema Pahwa, Manjot Singh, Ranjan Raj among many others. 

Produced by Shobha Kapoor, Ektaa R Kapoor’s Balaji Telefilms, Dream Girl 2 releases on August 25, 2023.

Starcast: Ayushmann Khurrana as Karam, Ananya Panday as Pari, Annu Kapoor as Jagjeet Singh, Paresh Rawal as Abu Saleem, Vijay Raaz as Sona Bhai, Rajpal Yadav as Shoukiya, Asrani Saab as Yusuf Ali Salim Khan, Manoj Joshi as Jaipal Srivastav, Abhishek Banerjee as Shahrukh, Seema Pahwa as Jumani, Manjot Singh as Smiley Dhillon, Ranjan Raj as Tiger Pandey

snippet.title: Sirf Tum Mega Episode 23 - [Eng Sub] - Anmol Baloch - Hamza Sohail - Mohsin Abbas - 6th Aug 2023
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Sirf Tum Mega Episode 23 - [Eng Sub] - Anmol Baloch - Hamza Sohail - Mohsin Abbas Haider - 6th Aug 2023 - Har Pal Geo

"Sirf Tum" revolves around Abeer who has recently returned from abroad to live with her extended family. Abeer's perspective on life and her priorities are different from her family's, which leads to conflict between them. Her cousins, Hanan and Hamza, are also part of this extended family.

Hamza is a rebellious and unconventional person who dreams of living life without any responsibilities or restrictions. In contrast, Hanan is a mature and sensible man who believes in love and relationships. After a series of events, Abeer and Hamza are set to marry. However, Hamza's inappropriate demands and unreasonable behaviour towards Abeer cause her to back out from the wedding. This creates chaos in the family and creates tension between Hamza & Abeer.
Ultimately, Hanan and Abeer are forced to marry each other. Though they reluctantly start their new life together, their past traumas continue to haunt them. The question remains: will Hanan and Abeer be able to overcome their past and find love for each other? Or will their differences and past experiences lead to further conflict and separation?

Written by: Seema Munaf
Directed by: Mazhar Moin
Produced by: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi

snippet.title: The Student Anthem Lyrical Song || Shanmukh Jaswanth || Infinitum Media
snippet.description:
From one take to another. Making memories and stories. 
Get ready to witness some serious nostalgia.

Cast:- Shanmukh Jaswanth, Don Pruthvi, Pruthvi Jhakaas, Neha Pathan, Tanuja Madhurapantula, Tejaswini Naidu, Sathwik Somalanka, Naga Vedith, Devesh, Vijay Arun Cr, Pranaya Vamsi, Madhu Nekkalapudi, Pranaya Vamsy Rambhatla(PVR).

Produced by Infinitum​ Network Solutions.

Sung by AniVee & Inno Genga

Rap performed by Sambhavam & AniVee

Lyrics by Kadali

Composed, arranged and programmed by AniVee

Guitars - Chris Jason

Bass Guitar - Reshwin Nishith & Chris Jason

Xylophone by Joseph Carpenter 

Afro percussion by Javed Adebayo

Gang Vocals by Svarathmika Sureshkumar, Srividhya, Dinesh Mohan, Nandha Visakan and Philomena

Mixed & Mastered by Rupendar Venkatesh at Mix Magic Studios

Written by  Subbu.K

Directed by Avinash 

Cinematography: Vamsi Srinivas 

Music: Anivee

Song Written by AniVee, Kadali

Lyric Video composition: Hemant korimi

Costume Designer: Sriya Patel

Line Producer: Siva Geddam - Mohan Reddy

Executive Producer: Rahul Raghavendra 

Brands Manager: Bhargav.T

#StudentAnthemLyricalSong #StudentWebseries #ShanmukhJaswanth #InfinitumMedia

Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/InfinitumOriginals
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/infinitum_originals/

►*About*
-------------
RadhaKrishn ke shaashwat prem ke vishay mein to sabhi ko gyaat hai. Radha bina Krishn nahin aur Krishn bina nahin Radha! Yadi Krishn Hriday hain, to Radha us hriday ki gati. Is premi yugal ki is mahagaatha mein aap jaanenge ki kis tarah Radha aur Krishn ne apne prem ko sansaar mein sthaapit kiya aur samast sansaar ko prem ki paribhasha sikhaayi, kyonki prem to bahut se log karte hain kintu keval prem ko paane ke liye… parantu RadhaKrishn ka prem ek-doosre ko paane ke liye nahin, apitu sansaar ko prem sikhaane ke liye tha. To dekhte rahiye RadhaKrishn ki ye anokhi prem-gaatha, jo Krishn nahin, apitu Radha ki drishti se likhee gayi hai!

English Translation 
The loving heart
In gentle tones it whispers
Hush dear, sleep

This warm, safe haven
Came to me as a blessing
Hush dear, sleep

The torment you endured
When you were only but a child 
No one told me ever

You may plead, you may fear
But it is love though that conquers

Where can light disappear?
Towards you, it will always veer

When these clouds of different shades gather together,          I see that there are no faults whatever!
The loving heart
In gentle tones it whispers
Hush dear, sleep

This warm, safe haven
Came to me as a blessing
Hush dear, sleep
 A flash at edge of the eye

As the blush of fresh nectar in a fluttering flower
It spreads wings everywhere
You lovely fragrance soothes like a mother
And plants gentle kisses on the forehead

For you are the melody
in the midst of a blazing forest

I soar to the skies this day
I bask in the dazzling moonlight

In my heart, sparkles galore of varied hues
A peppy number sets me to groove

When you come near, O sweet heart
There is a deluge of golden star bursts

When you are my warm haven
These thorns I tread drip honey

O sweetheart, O sugar candy,
Shower me with your breathless kisses

O sweetheart, O sugar candy,
Lead me into the flowering wilderness
Lead me into the flowering wilderness

Produced By -  Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #SAB

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Click here to watch the episode of TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah: 
https://youtube.com/playlist?list=PL6Rtnh6YJK7ZFhouqhrvP3Sx0U7qxdzJi

snippet.title: Bank Loan के चक्रव्यूह में फंसा Jetha | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Bank Story
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to LIV Comedy: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCBIT1FSJW6yTlzqK-31FDWg?sub_confirmation=1

Taarak Mehta and Bhide are upset about the recent bank fraud which took place in one of the banks. They have a full-fledged discussion on it. On the other hand, bank employees from two different banks come to visit Jethalal as he has taken loans from those banks. Seeing him take loan, Champaklal gets furious and he starts to question Jethalal. Stay tuned to get your daily dose of laughter.

Show Name - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast - Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt
Episode - 2495
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi, Neela Asit Modi

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #livcomedy #tmkoc #comedy2023 #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #comedy #jethalal #taarakmehta 

About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in 'Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

Click here to watch all the fun episodes of TMKOC - Bank Story: 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLSXTaG1fT0cR9p9VQwjI5aMs4C7SD5EYS

snippet.title: भारत की सबसे बड़ी मंडी, आज़ादपुर में मंदी | Rahul Gandhi
snippet.description:
मंडी में मंदी क्यों? - आज़ादपुर मंडी में मज़दूरों, व्यापारियों और किसानों से एक मुलाकात! 

किसानों से उपभोगताओं तक फसल पहुंचने के बीच एक लंबी कड़ी होती है जिसको सुनना, जिसके संघर्षों को जानना बहुत ज़रूरी है। यात्रा के क्रम को बढ़ाते हुए, इस कड़ी को जोड़ने हम आज़ादपुर मंडी पहुंचे।

भारत की इस सबसे पुरानी और सबसे बड़ी सब्ज़ी मंडी में काम कभी रुकता नहीं। ट्रकों का आना जाना, मज़दूरों का शोर, व्यापारियों का हिसाब, यह सब हर वक्त चालू रहता है।

मुलाकात के दौरान मंडी में काम करने वाले हर वर्ग से मेरी बात हुई। सबकी अपनी अपनी समस्याएं मगर फिर भी एक दूसरे से जुड़ी हुईं। जहां व्यापारी GST और महंगाई से परेशान दिखे वहीं मज़दूर महंगाई के साथ बेरोज़गारी से।

जटाशंकर एक मज़दूर हैं, जो इस काम के कारण एक साल से ज़्यादा से घर नहीं जा पाए हैं, अपने परिवार से नहीं मिल पाए हैं। जाएं भी तो कैसे, काम छूटा तो पैसे कट जाएंगे और इस महंगाई में गुज़ारा और मुश्किल हो जाएगा। नुकसान के कारण कई रातें वैसे भी भूखे गुज़र जाती हैं।

एक व्यापारी केवलानंद लोहनी सुबह 2 बजे से काम पर पहुंच जाते हैं - कहते हैं UPA की सरकार में बचत हो जाती थी, मौजूदा सरकार में उल्टा नुकसान हो रहा है। बच्चे चाहते हैं वो ये काम न करें, मगर उनके पास रोज़गार के अवसर भी नहीं हैं।

आज़ादपुर मंडी की सबसे खास बात यहां का सद्भाव है, हर धर्म, हर जात, हर प्रांत के लोग यहां मिल जुल कर काम करते हैं। आपस में मुकाबला भी है तो सम्मान के साथ। उनके शब्दों में, ये व्यापार व्यवहार से चलता है।

ये कड़ी एक पहेली सी लगती है, मगर उन्हें अगर सुना जाए, उनकी बात समझी जाए तो इनकी समस्याएं भी वही हैं जो पूरे देश की हैं, और उनका उपाय भी - महंगाई और बेरोज़गारी का अंत।

#rahulgandhi, #राहुल_गांधी, #bharatjodoyatra

snippet.title: Grilled fruits Fruits BBQ
snippet.description:
In this video we will see how to make a grilled fruits BBQ recipe in tamil. Grilling causes caramelization of sugars and adds a sweet caramel flavor. Even fruits which have a very mild sweet taste will get a lot sweeter after grilling them. Pineapple and watermelon are always perfect for grilling. Grilling over charcoal slowly brings up the heat and creates the perfect conditions for caramelization.
#grilledfruits #grilledrecipes 

Friends, please do try this grilled fruits recipe at home and share it with your friends and family. Also, please do share your feedback about the recipe in the comments below. All the best and happy cooking!!


For simple sugar syrup:
1/2 cup Sugar
1/2 cup Water

Subscribe To Shemaroo Movie in Parts: https://www.youtube.com/user/shemaroopremiumfilms?sub_confirmation=1

Movie Name - Kaali Topi Laal Rumaal (2000)
Star Cast - Mithun Chakraborty, Kamal Sadanah, Rituparna Sengupta, Ranjeet, Zeenat Ibrahim, Mohan Joshi, Johnny Lever 
Director –  B Vijay Reddy
Producer – Lal Purswani
Music Director –  Dilip Sen, Sameer Sen
Cinematographer – Ashok Rao
Lyricist –  Rani Malik, Maya Govind, Nawab Arzoo
Writer - Qamar Jaladabadi
Editor – V.N. Mayekar

Kaali Topi Laal Rumaal is the story of Commando Vijay, who becomes an Army officer, despite of the problems in his childhood. He singlehandedly captures a terrorist named Master D.D, and holds him in a cell. What Vijay does not know is that Master D.D is a mere pawn, and the real kingpin is an unknown assailant known only as Kaali Topi Laal Rumaal. Will Vijay be able to make the country and his parents proud of him with his service?

#KaaliTopiLaalRumaal #MithunChakraborty  #kamalsadanah 

फिल्म का नाम - काली टोपी लाल रुमाल (2000)
स्टार कास्ट - मिथुन चक्रवर्ती, कमल सदाना, रितुपर्णा सेनगुप्ता, रंजीत, जीनत इब्राहिम, मोहन जोशी, जॉनी लीवर
निदेशक - बी विजय रेड्डी
निर्माता - लाल पुरसवानी
संगीत निर्देशक - दिलीप सेन, समीर सेन
छायाकार - अशोक राव
गीतकार - रानी मलिक, माया गोविंद, नवाब आरज़ू
लेखक- क़मर जलादाबादी
संपादक - वी.एन. मायेकर

काली टोपी लाल रुमाल कमांडो विजय की कहानी है, जो बचपन में समस्याओं के बावजूद एक सेना अधिकारी बन जाता है। वह अकेले ही मास्टर डी.डी. नाम के एक आतंकवादी को पकड़ लेता है और उसे एक कोठरी में बंद कर देता है। विजय को यह नहीं पता कि मास्टर डी.डी. एक मोहरा मात्र है, और असली सरगना एक अज्ञात हमलावर है जिसे काली टोपी लाल रुमाल के नाम से जाना जाता है। क्या विजय अपनी सेवा से देश और अपने माता-पिता को उस पर गर्व कर पाएगा?

#KaaliTopiLaalRumaal #MithunChakraborty #kamalsadanah

*About* 
------------

           Yeh kahani hai ek sidhi sadhi, padhi likhi, pyaari si, Pratigya aur ameer, bigdel, badtameez Krishna ki. Pratigya ki parvarish hui ek sadharan par acche parivaar mein jaha padhai aur sanskaron ko diya gaya bohot mahatva. Wahi doosri taraf apne parivaar mein Krishna ne dekhi zulm aur paise ki taakat. Isi taakat ke dum par zabardasti ki Krishna ne Pratigya se shaadi. 
           Pratigya ke sasural aur maayke mein hai zameen aur aasmaan ka faasla. Krishna ki haveli mein prem aur aadar ka hai akaal. Aise mein kya hoga Pratigya ka haal? Waqt ke sath Pratigya- Krishna ne kiya hazaaron mushkilon ka saamna aur door hua dono ke beech ka faasla. Ek anchaha rishta ban gaya sacche pyaar ki misaal.
